we have to figure out

849
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:59,760
whether there's a land deed in that box.

850
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:01,030
If there is,

851
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:03,050
we should quickly transfer it
into your name—

852
00:42:03,050 --> 00:42:04,510
or destroy it

853
00:42:04,530 --> 00:42:05,980
and reissue a new one.

854
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,480
The most important thing right now

855
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:08,730
is to sell this house

856
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:09,800
and get the money.

857
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,280
And if we're lucky,

858
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:13,070
maybe besides the land deed,

859
00:42:13,150 --> 00:42:15,210
there are gold bars or US dollars inside.

860
00:42:15,210 --> 00:42:16,400
Then all our financial problems

861
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:17,730
will be totally solved.

862
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,150
What kind of luck did
our Zhang family ancestors

863
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,760
have to have married

864
00:42:25,230 --> 00:42:27,400
such a capable wife like you?

865
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,480
Where's Wanfu?

866
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:35,230
Inside.

867
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,000
Thanks.

868
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,030
Wanfu!

869
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:38,030
Wanfu!

870
00:42:38,250 --> 00:42:38,990
Wanfu!

871
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:40,000
Why are you here?

872
00:42:40,070 --> 00:42:41,140
I found a job.

873
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:42,190
You found a job?

874
00:42:42,230 --> 00:42:44,280
A guide at Hujiang Guide Agency.

875
00:42:44,560 --> 00:42:45,290
A...

876
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:47,320
Basically, I introduce Shanghai's customs

877
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:48,960
and local culture to tourists,

878
00:42:48,960 --> 00:42:49,670
and tell them

879
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:51,190
where the good food and fun places are.

880
00:42:51,190 --> 00:42:53,230
One yuan per hour.

881
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,190
One yuan?

882
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,700
If I speak English,

883
00:42:56,040 --> 00:42:56,970
it's double pay.

884
00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:58,010
This...

885
00:42:58,530 --> 00:42:59,150
Look.

886
00:42:59,330 --> 00:43:00,820
[Hujiang Guide Agency]

887
00:43:02,250 --> 00:43:03,840
How can there be such a good thing?
